data.description: PICK ME! PICK ME! A small grassy hill on a winding, shady tree-lined street is the picturesque site of this 3 or 4 bedroom, 2 bath brick home eagerly awaiting its new owners. Located within quick walking distance from Pineville Junior High School on a almost half-acre lot, this charming home offers a wonderful and convenient lifestyle with sparkling new bathrooms, neutral colors, wood, tile and laminate flooring, newer ceiling fans in nearly every room and a floor plan that can be used in multiple ways. What was designed originally as the living and dining rooms has been enjoyed as a bedroom and a playroom in recent years.  Even the storage room with its almost new 73-gallon hot water heater is heated and cooled. The oversized utility room has plentiful storage cabinets and adjoins another area that could be used as an office, indoor patio or other. The fully fenced backyard is accented by a brick patio, storage shed and offers room to breathe and enjoy the outdoor lifestyle. New architectural shingle roof in 2020.  Refrigerator remains. New flooring installed (carpet removed) in one bedroom Jan. 2024.
